Package oracle.apps.fnd.appltest.diagfwk.cli

Class Summary
ArgProcessor A utility class that processes the command-line arguments in the form of a String array to a well defined "verb" and associated name value parameters required for executing the verb.
BaseVerb Models a verb supported by the Diagnostics Command-Line interface.
DiagControl This class is the entry point for the diagnostics engine through the command line.
ExtractMetadataVerb Verb for extracting XML test metadata from the test repository.
HelpVerb  
QueryVerb Verb for browsing the test repository for available tests.
RegisterVerb Verb for registering tests with the test repository.
ReportVerb Verb for extracting reports for one or more test executions.
RunTestVerb Verb for executing one or more tests.
StatusVerb Verb for checking the status for a particular test run or execution.
StdInUtil Utlity APIs for reading from standard input
